To build bfilter:

    make

To run the test suite:

    make check

To install as a local program, from a root shell, or prefix each command
with ``sudo``:

    cp bfilter /usr/local/bin
    cp bfilter.1 /usr/local/share/man/man1

To install as a system program, from a root shell, or prefix each
command with ``sudo``:

    cp bfilter /usr/bin
    cp bfilter.1 /usr/share/man/man1

In case of any problems, please contact me via email:

    toby@paccrat.org

Or via the github page:

    https://github.com/TobyGoodwin/bfilter
